# PR Screenshots with Playwright

When UI files are modified (under `ui/components/`, `ui/pages/`, `*.tsx`, `*.scss`), **always suggest capturing before/after screenshots** for the PR.

## Screenshots folder

```bash
mkdir -p .pr-screenshots   # gitignored — safe to write here
```

## Capture a screenshot

Playwright (`@playwright/test`) is already installed — no extra install needed:

```bash
# Full page
npx playwright screenshot <url> .pr-screenshots/<slug>.png

# Examples
npx playwright screenshot http://localhost:9011 .pr-screenshots/storybook-component.png
npx playwright screenshot http://localhost:8080 .pr-screenshots/dapp-before.png
```

## Available dev servers

| Server | Port | Start command |
|---|---|---|
| Test dapp | `:8080` | `yarn dapp` |
| Storybook | `:9011` | `yarn storybook` |
| Extension popup | Load via `chrome://extensions` | `yarn start` |

## Embed in PR description

Place under `## **Screenshots/Recordings**` in the MetaMask PR template:

```markdown
### **Before**
![description](.pr-screenshots/before.png)

### **After**
![description](.pr-screenshots/after.png)
```

## Rule

- ALWAYS suggest screenshots when `ui/` files are changed
- NEVER commit `.pr-screenshots/` (it is gitignored)
- Prefer Storybook (`:9011`) for component-level shots; test dapp (`:8080`) for flow-level shots
